In collaboration with the Pop Hop Bookshop, Avenue 50 Studio is delighted to host Suzanne Lummis&#8217; Poetry Reading and Book Signing. 
 &nbsp; 
 Suzanne Lummis&#8217; fourth collection,  Crime Wave  (Giant Claw,Fall 2025) was included in Literary Hub&#8217;s  100 Notable Small Press Books 2025  and described as &#8220;Savvy, robust and relentless.&#8221; She’s the editor of the new anthology  Poetry Goes to the Movies  (Pacific Coast Poetry Series) .  Poetry.la produces her seriocomic YouTube series, They Write by Night, on poetry and film noir.   She received her MA from CSU Fresno where she studied with the renowned poet and teacher Philip Levine, later a U.S. Poet Laureate. Her poems have appeared in New Ohio Review, Plume, Catamaran, Rattle, and The New Yorker. She&#8217;s an influe
